{
  "id": "adv_main_01_17_04",
  "title": "星見編4章9話",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_way-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "01-3d",
      "startTime": null
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_street-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_17_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_17_04-ktn001.m4a",
      "text": "……アイドルって、なんなんでしょうね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What even is an idol‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 2.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_17_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_17_04-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "また、難しい質問するな\n……確かに、なんなんだろう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You keep giving me tough questions.\nTrue… What is an idol?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 9.833333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_17_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_17_04-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "（歌手ともタレントとも違う、けど人の心に訴えかける）\n（何かがアイドルにはある。不思議な存在だ）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(Idols are different from singers or celebrities‚ but they do appeal to people’s hearts.)\n(Idols have a certain special something. They’re enigmas.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 17.633333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_17_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_17_04-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "お姉ちゃんは、どう思っていたんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What did my sister think?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 22.633333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_17_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_17_04-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "さあ……分からない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I don’t know.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 25.333333333333332,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_17_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_17_04-ktn003.m4a",
      "text": "聞いたことないんですか？\n一緒に仕事していたのに",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You never asked her?\nBut you worked together.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 30.433333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_17_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_17_04-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "考えてみたら、聞いたことないな\nでも多分、麻奈自身も分かってなかったんじゃないかな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Come to think of it‚ I never asked her.\nBut I doubt Mana herself even knew the answer.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 36.36666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_17_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_17_04-ktn004.m4a",
      "text": "そうですかね……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You think so?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 40.56666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_17_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_17_04-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "そんなこと言葉にして、何か意味あるのかって\n言いそうな気がする",
      "translations": {
        "en": "“What’s the point in putting that into words anyway?”\nI get the feeling that’s what she’d say.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 46.266666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_17_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_17_04-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "それより、もっと沢山歌いたい\nステージに立ちたい、みんなと一緒に笑いたい……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "“I’d rather just sing a lot.”\n“I want to be on stage. I want to smile with everyone.”",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 51.03333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_17_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_17_04-ktn005.m4a",
      "text": "ふふっ、言いそうですね。お姉ちゃん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hehe‚ yeah‚ my sister would say that.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 55.333333333333336,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_17_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_17_04-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "……本人に聞いてみないのか？\n麻奈なら、いるぞ。まだ俺の側に",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Won’t you just ask her directly?\nMana’s here right now. She’s right next to me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 62.56666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_17_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_17_04-ktn006.m4a",
      "text": "…………幻じゃなくて\n本当にいるんですね……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "She’s not an illusion…\nShe really is here‚ isn’t she?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 68.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_17_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_17_04-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "最初はそう思ったよ。自分にだけ見えている幻だって\nでも、そうじゃなかった",
      "translations": {
        "en": "At first‚ I thought she was an illusion—one only I could see.\nBut I was wrong.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 75.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_17_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_17_04-ktn007.m4a",
      "text": "お姉ちゃん、なんで幽霊になって現れたんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Why do you think my sister came back as a ghost?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 77.96666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_17_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_17_04-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "言ってたこともあるけど、多分それは冗談で\nどうしてもグランプリの決勝のステージに立ちたいと",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But I have a feeling that was a joke.\nShe said she was determined to stand on stage at the Grand Prix finals.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 81.96666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_17_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_17_04-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "……きっと\n琴乃のことが心配だったんじゃないかな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m sure\nit’s because she was worried about you‚ Kotono.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 90.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_17_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_17_04-ktn008.m4a",
      "text": "……私を？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "About me?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 93.23333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_17_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_17_04-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "そんなに意外か？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Is it really that hard to believe?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 94.96666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_17_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_17_04-ktn009.m4a",
      "text": "もちろん気にしてくれてはいると思うけど\nだったら私の所に現れるのが普通だと思いませんか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Of course I assumed she cared about me‚\nbut‚ in that case‚ wouldn’t you expect her to appear to me as a ghost?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 100.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_17_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_17_04-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "それは……確かに……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah… you have a point.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 104.03333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_17_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_17_04-ktn010.m4a",
      "text": "お姉ちゃん、自分のために何かするより\n誰かのために何かすることが大好きだったから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "My sister never did things for herself.\nShe loved doing things for others.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 110.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_17_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_17_04-ktn011.m4a",
      "text": "……きっと、幽霊になって現れたのも\n私以外の誰かのためだと思いますよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m sure the reason she came back as a ghost\nwas for someone else besides me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 117.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_17_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_17_04-ktn012.m4a",
      "text": "……昔……あ、お姉ちゃんがアイドルになる少し前\nですけど、私、クラスでラブレターもらって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Long ago… oh‚ I mean‚ this happened a little before she became an idol‚\nI got a love letter from someone in my class.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 124.76666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_17_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_17_04-koh013.m4a",
      "text": "おお、何、その面白そうな話題",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Whoa! This sounds like a juicy story.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 129.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_17_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_17_04-ktn013.m4a",
      "text": "茶化すのなら話しません",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I won’t tell you if you’re gonna make fun of me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 133.23333333333332,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_17_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_17_04-koh014.m4a",
      "text": "あ、いや冗談冗談。何？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ uh‚ I was just kidding. What happened?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 135.36666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_17_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_17_04-ktn014.m4a",
      "text": "それで困ってお姉ちゃんに相談して……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I didn’t know what to do‚ so I asked my sister about it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 139.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_17_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_17_04-ktn015.m4a",
      "text": "その時、話の流れで聞いたことあるんです\nお姉ちゃん、好きな人いるのって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And during our conversation‚ I asked her a question.\nI asked her if she had a crush on someone.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 146.63333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_nagaseliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "02-2d",
      "startTime": 150.13333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_nagaseliving-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "02-2d",
      "startTime": 150.13333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_heart-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 150.36666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_17_04/sud_vo_adv_main_01_17_04-mna001.m4a",
      "text": "いるよー",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Of course I do.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 151.16666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
